The OpenIE-based methods, Quasimodo and StereoKG, produce the shortest assertion (32 and 37 characters on average, respectively). The manually-constructed KG (Acharya et al.) has the longest assertions (102 characters). \systemname{}, having average assertion lengths (69 and 73), stands between those two approaches.